    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document modifies the "Unassigned" number space in the IANA "OSPFv3 Instance ID Address Family Values" registry by dividing it in two halves -- one half Unassigned but managed via Standards Action, and the other Reserved for Private Use.  It updates RFC 5838.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
